extracted_text: (5) Lot area. For each dwelling, and building accessory thereto, there shall be lot area of not less than 9,000 square feet.
(97) Driveways and sidewalks. An improved impervious driveway shall be constructed for each dwelling unit, and each driveway shall include enough area for two parking spaces.
llm_outputs.rationale: The extracted text provides the information about the minimum lot area required for each dwelling and the requirement for an improved impervious driveway for each dwelling unit that includes enough area for two parking spaces. This information pertains to the parking requirements for single-family homes in the C-2 General Commercial District.
